com.spotify.apollo.route

Interface VersionedRoute


  • public interface VersionedRoute
    Defines a possibly open-ended range of versions in which a particular Route should be available. A com.spotify.apollo.route.VersionedRoute with an empty value for removedIn() is valid from validFrom() inclusive up to the latest version of the API. A com.spotify.apollo.route.VersionedRoute with a value for removedIn() is valid in the range [validFrom(), removedIn()). That is, removedIn() defines the first version in which it is no longer valid.
